<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV82">
<l>erikoḷcen nāyi ṟiraṇṭuṭa ṉēyuta yammalaivāy</l>
<l>virikiṉṟa vaṇṇatta vemperu māṉkaṇkaḷ mīṇṭavaṟṟu</l>
<l>ḷerikoḷcen tīvī ḻacuraraip pōlavem pōliyarkkum</l>
<l>virivacol līritu vōvaiya muṟṟum viḷariyatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The rising of two flaming red suns together, of the colour that expands on the</l>
<l>mountain, the eyes of our great lord, [for us] to resemble the Asuras</l>
<l>that fall again into them, into the flaming red fire, for the likes of us</l>
<l>they open. Speak: is it this the whole world calls for?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
